Hi Tosin
Well... I’m assuming it’s the same as in other industries but haven’t dabbled enough to know for sure
It’s a majority of males in artist roles but majority of females in production so you don’t lack contact with either gender 
I’ve been sexually harassed by a superior and it was awful and I told no one because I didn’t think anyone would believe me/ care (I was in a runner role) 
He’s since long and I don’t think in the current climate I would’ve kept quiet but it could’ve happened anywhere really and nowadays I’m sure that if I’d spoken up something would’ve been done
Is this the things you’re asking?

I think you’ll have no shortage of female role models within the industry 
There’s a lot more of us now and there’s some true talented people
